Jessica Opare Saforo (amụrụ na 29 Eprel 1981) bụ onye mgbasa ozi Ghana, onye mgbasa ozi  igwe onyonyo na redio na onye ọchụnta ego. Ọzọkwa, ọ bụ onye na-ahụ maka Transformation with Jess, ihe ngosi  igwe onyonyo mbụ nke Ghana. Ọ bụ onye nwe ụlọ ọrụ The Voice Ova Company, ụlọ ọrụ na-ahụ maka ijikwa talent olu.
Saforo gụrụ akwụkwọ sekọndrị na Akosombo International School ma nwekwa nzere bachelọ na nka na Mahadum Ghana, Legon ebe ọ gụrụ na Economics na Psychology.
